                <bibl>again Morelli, <ptr target="#SECir"/>, <citedRange>259</citedRange> (no image) as unpublished</bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>063600</citedRange></bibl>.
                Cf. <bibl><ptr target="#marengo1985"/><citedRange/></bibl>, whence 
                <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>36.1461</citedRange></bibl>;
                <bibl><ptr target="#rosamilia2014"/>, n. <citedRange>13</citedRange></bibl>, whence
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>64.2012</citedRange></bibl>. 
                </p>
